FBIS3-60211 "jptdd004__l94061" JPRS-TDD-94-004-L Document Type:JPRS Document Title:Narcotics 26 January 1994 WEST EUROPE GREECE Italian Arrested With Over 3 Kg of Heroin NC2301194094 Athens ATHENS NEWS in English 23 Jan 94 p 1 NC2301194094 Athens ATHENS NEWS Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] Over 3 kilos of heroin were seized by police yesterday and an Italian arrested. Pasquale Palumbo told customs authorities at the Greek-Turkish border that he had nothing to declare. But a thorough search of his car revealed a 3.150 kilos of heroin. The drugs were discovered packed in 12 small packages and hidden in the car's footboards. Four or five grams of hashish were also found in Palumbo's pockets. Customs authorities confiscated the drugs and Palumbo was taken to Alexandroupoli's court in Thrace.
